{
  "stem": "7157.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we finally settled in a town called Stanislawow, which incidentally today-- it's so far east that today it's actually part of the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it's not even Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in those days, in 1939, it was-- it was Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- for part of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they settled in a different city then Stanislawow, my grandfather and grandmother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where we were in Stanislawow, which was a big city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was still-- we were still pretty much a family unit-- my father, my mother, my brother, and I.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were some other relatives but basically those.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandparents stayed in a little town nearby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, they wanted the kids-- which is George and me-- but I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my brother went over there for a little while to make it kind of easier for my mother to only have one child at a time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And now we're into 1940 and pushing 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is, of course, when the war really started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, the bombing started happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I recall-- and this I recall very vividly-- being in this little apartment in Stanislawow for-- everybody was running down to the cellar, because there was bombs hitting.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my father was not feeling well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He couldn't go down the cellar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He already had evidently angina or some form of heart-- he was very-- he was quite ill.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed upstairs in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember I was helping even-- my mother got somebody to help us, but I was basically helping to put a big couch up against the window, because you know, so you wouldn't have glass shattered.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shattering.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, if a bomb hit that building, there wasn't much you could do.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
